N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 18 §§ 358-2.28 - Notice of missed interview

State Regulations

Notice of missed interview means a notice sent by a
social services district informing an applicant or recipient that they have
missed a scheduled food stamp eligibility or recertification interview and
advising them that it is their responsibility to reschedule the
interview. Notes
